Titolo: Bomberman Tournament

Anno: 2001

Descrizione: Bomberman Tournament is a game in the Bomberman series for the GBA. The game contains a multiplayer battle mode between linked Game Boy Advances. The player and up to three others can compete in any of the game's eight multiplayer battle arenas, each of which has its own unique gameplay twist.



Genere: Action-adventure 

Valutazione: N/A
